protective_factors: Explicitly denies intent or plan (I couldn't do that to them)
Identifies family/children as reasons for living
Engaged in treatment (agreed to medication change)
risk_factors: Current severe, active depressive episode (F33.1 Moderate)
Anhedonia/Avolition leading to impaired functioning (missing work)
Feelings of guilt and hopelessness ('I'm a failure')
clinical_actions: Safety planning review to reinforce protective factors
